              <p class="text-white">
                Creating an active and fun learning environment for children involves turning education into an exciting adventure, where curiosity is sparked, and knowledge is gained through interactive and enjoyable activities. It's all about making learning a thrilling journey filled with discovery and joy!
              </p>
              <% if user_signed_in? %>
                <%= link_to "Your account", manage_children_path, class:"w-25 btn btn-primary" %>
              <% else %>
                <%= link_to "Sign up today", new_user_registration_path, class:"w-25 btn btn-primary" %>
              <% end %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-1"></div>
            <div class="col-4 pt-5">
              <%= image_tag "caro1.png", class:"w-100" %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item" id="carousel-item-container">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row pt-5">
            <!-- Header and button inside the carousel item -->
            <div class="col-6 d-flex justify-content-center flex-column ps-5 carousel-text text-white">
              <h2 id="carousel-h2"><strong>Get more connected to your child</strong></h2>
              <p class="text-white">
                Deepening your connection with your child means fostering meaningful moments through open communication and shared activities. It's about building a strong bond that goes beyond words, creating a closeness that lasts a lifetime!
              </p>
              <% if user_signed_in? %>
                <%= link_to "Your account", manage_children_path, class:"w-25 btn btn-primary" %>
              <% else %>
                <%= link_to "Sign up today", new_user_registration_path, class:"w-25 btn btn-primary" %>
